flowchart TD
    SRC["Runtime fault detected"] --> TYPE{"Fault type"}

    TYPE -->|invalid sensor value| SV["Set sensor error flag<br/>use last valid value"]
    TYPE -->|command timeout| CF["esp_hardware failsafe<br/>all actuators off"]
    TYPE -->|stale sensor data| SD["esp_logic safe command<br/>fan, pump and alarm off"]
    TYPE -->|WiFi startup error| WF["Log error<br/>continue control tasks"]
    TYPE -->|task stack low| ST["Watchdog logs warning"]

    SV --> VIS["Visible in serial logs<br/>and UART status frame"]
    CF --> VIS
    SD --> VIS
    WF --> VIS
    ST --> VIS
